'''達雷爾·卡斯特'''（{{lang-en|Darrell Castle}}；{{bd|1948年10月11日||}}），是一名美國[[曼非斯_(田納西州)|田納西州曼非斯]]的政治人物、活動家和[[律師|律師]]，在[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]成為[[憲法黨_(美國)|憲法黨]][[美国总统|总统]]候選人<ref name="CastleIsPrez">{{cite web|url=http://www.independentpoliticalreport.com/2016/04/darrell-castle-wins-the-constitution-partys-presidential-nomination/|title=Darrell Castle wins the Constitution Party’s presidential nomination|last=Lesiak|first=Krzyszof|date=April 16, 2016|publisher=''[[Independent_Political_Report|Independent Political Report]]''|accessdate=2016-04-16|archive-date=2018-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008100036/http://independentpoliticalreport.com/2016/04/darrell-castle-wins-the-constitution-partys-presidential-nomination/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦曾在[[2008年美國總統選舉|2008年美國總統選舉]]擔任憲法黨[[美国副总统|副总统]]候選人<ref name="CastleIsVP">{{cite web|url=http://www.ballot-access.org/2008/04/26/darrell-castle-is-constitution-party-vice-presidential-nominee/|title=Darrell Castle is Constitution Party Vice-Presidential Nominee|last=Winger|first=Richard|date=April 26, 2008|publisher=''[[Ballot_Access_News|Ballot Access News]]''|accessdate=2008-11-12|archive-date=2018-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180830174218/http://ballot-access.org/2008/04/26/darrell-castle-is-constitution-party-vice-presidential-nominee/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==2016年總統競選==
卡斯特是憲法黨2016年總統候選人提名的候選人，但在2016年1月由於不明健康問題撤回他的提名<ref>{{cite web |author=Posted on |url=http://ballot-access.org/2016/01/06/darrell-castle-withdraws-from-constitution-party-presidential-nomination-race/ |title=Darrell Castle Withdraws from Constitution Party Presidential Nomination Race |publisher=Ballot Access News |date=2016-01-06 |accessdate=2016-08-03 |archive-date=2016-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804024334/http://ballot-access.org/2016/01/06/darrell-castle-withdraws-from-constitution-party-presidential-nomination-race/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而在{{le|憲法黨全國代表大會|Constitution Party National Convention|2016年憲法黨全國代表大會}}前夕，《{{le|投票訪問新聞|Ballot Access News}}》的{{le|理查德·溫格|Richard Winger}}報導指出卡斯特已再次進入提名程序<ref>{{cite news|url=http://ballot-access.org/2016/04/12/joe-miller-decides-not-to-seek-constitution-party-presidential-nomination/|title=Joe Miller Decides Not to Seek Constitution Party Presidential Nomination|date=April 12, 2016|accessdate=13 April 2016|archive-date=2020-09-09|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200909165740/http://ballot-access.org/2016/04/12/joe-miller-decides-not-to-seek-constitution-party-presidential-nomination/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年4月16日，卡斯特確定獲得憲法黨總統候選人提名<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://www.mwcnews.net/news/americas/58393-constitution-party-candidate.html|title=US: Darrell Castle named Constitution Party candidate|last=Agencies|website=www.mwcnews.net|access-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423174524/http://www.mwcnews.net/news/americas/58393-constitution-party-candidate.html|archive-date=2016-04-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，他發誓一旦當選，將讓美國脫離[[聯合國|聯合國]]和[[北大西洋公约组织|北大西洋公约组织]]<ref name=":0" />。他在演說中表示「我們的邊界值得捍衛。如果我們能確保韓國和德國的邊界，那麼我們就可以保證美國的邊界。」（Our borders are worth defending. If we can secure the borders of Korea and Germany, then we can secure the borders of the United States）<ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=http://www.good4utah.com/news/local-news/the-constitution-party-hosts-national-convention-in-salt-lake-city|title=The Constitution Party hosts national convention in Salt Lake City|last=Mills|first=Glen|website=GOOD4UTAH|language=en-US|access-date=2016-04-24|archive-date=2016-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160726214019/http://www.good4utah.com/news/local-news/the-constitution-party-hosts-national-convention-in-salt-lake-city|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，不過他沒有提及以前的健康問題<ref name=":1" />。

卡斯特的競選活動已獲得{{le|佐治亚生命权|Georgia Right to Life}}[[政治行動委員會|政治行動委員會]]支持<ref>[http://grtlpac.org/pac-endorsements/ ''Endorsements – GRTL PAC''] {{Wayback|url=http://grtlpac.org/pac-endorsements/ |date=20210508122604 }}. ''Georgia Right to Life PAC''. Retrieved July 2, 2016.</ref>；截至2016年6月30日，他募集了$10,289捐款<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fec.gov/fecviewer/CandidateCommitteeDetail.do?candidateCommitteeId=P60021102&tabIndex=1 |title=Committee/Candidate Details |publisher=Fec.gov |date= |accessdate=2016-08-03 |archive-date=2016-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214033841/http://www.fec.gov/fecviewer/CandidateCommitteeDetail.do?candidateCommitteeId=P60021102&tabIndex=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

